{"title":"Bag an unmissable deal with Wiggle’s Black Friday promotion","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/sponsored/wiggle-black-friday-week-one-deals","date":1699006651000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/sponsored/wiggle-black-friday-week-one-deals\">Bag an unmissable deal with Wiggle’s Black Friday promotion</a></p>\n\n<p>Halloween, then Christmas, right? That’s the general scheme of end-of-year events and celebrations. Not this year! Online retailer Wiggle is offering something we can all get behind this November – a selection of weekly offers on some of the finest cycling kit, accessories, and even bikes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>These piping hot deals are being offered at up to 60% off the RRP, and you don’t even need to wait for Black Friday itself to bag yourself an early Christmas present or two – the savings you see here are all available from 9am on November 22 up to 4pm on November 29 at Wiggle’s dedicated <a href=\"http://www.wiggle.co.uk/black-friday\" target=\"_blank\">Black Friday home page</a>. Ready to load up on cut-price gear from some of the biggest names in cycling? Here’s our pick of Wiggle’s first week of deals…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Up to 60% off cycle clothing!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep yourself dry, snug – and particularly smug – with Wiggle’s extensive discounts on clothing. See the latest deals <a href=\"http://www.wiggle.com/m/black-friday-cycle?index=n&amp;categoryNames=Clothing&amp;sport=Cycle\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Castelli Alpha RoS 2 jacket – £176 (RRP £320) | SAVE £144!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"625\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-02-970x625.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-02-970x625.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-02-300x193.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-02-768x495.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-02-750x483.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-02-1140x734.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-02.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>The third generation of Italian brand Castelli’s renowned ‘Rain or Shine’ garment, this all-seasons jacket boasts the ideal combination of warmth, breathability and rain protection. Weatherproofing is courtesy of Gore-Tex Infinium Windstopper fabric, there are minimal seams, a vented back and a double-layer cuff to keep the weather at bay. There are also three pockets and an extra zipped compartment for essentials.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=BF+Email+-+Castelli+alpha+jacket&amp;ued=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Fcastelli-alpha-ros-2-jacket\" target=\"_blank\">Buy the Castelli Alpha RoS 2 jacket from Wiggle</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Endura Pro SL Bibshorts – £79.99 (RRP £139.99) | SAVE £60!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"712\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-03-970x712.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-03-970x712.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-03-300x220.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-03-768x564.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-03-750x551.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-03-1140x837.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-03.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Stock up now on some of the planet’s best cycling shorts and you’ll be ready for sunshine and dry roads come springtime. The Endura Pro SL bib shorts offer comfortable compression, breathable fabric and even lumbar support. What’s more, the 700 Series Pad II is one of the most comfortable chamois out there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=BF+Email+-+Endura+pro+bib+shorts&amp;ued=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Fendura-pro-sl-bib-shorts\" target=\"_blank\">Buy the Endura Pro SL Bibshorts from Wiggle</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Castelli Explore Velocissimo Bibtights – £70 (RRP £140) | SAVE £70!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"723\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-04-970x723.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-04-970x723.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-04-300x224.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-04-768x573.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-04-750x559.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-04-1140x850.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-04.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Protect your muscles and stay toasty when the temperature drops with these exceptional bib tights. Warmth is trapped by the Thermoflex fabric, seams are kept to a minimum, zippers at the ankles keep everything anchored in place and the Kiss Air 2 chamois is all-day-comfortable in the saddle.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=BF+Email+-+Castelli+explore+bib+tights&amp;ued=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Fcastelli-explore-velocissimo-bib-tights\" target=\"_blank\">Buy the Castelli Explore Velocissimo Bibtights from Wiggle</a></strong> </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Castelli Alpha RoS Light Jacket – £154 (RRP £280) | SAVE £126!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"565\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-05-970x565.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-05-970x565.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-05-300x175.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-05-768x447.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-05-750x437.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-05-1140x664.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-05.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Perfect for battling light rain, misty mornings and damp roads, this jacket has water-repellent material at the front and breathable fabric to the rear, so you’re kept dry in the drizzliest of conditions. A clever double-layer system allows you to unzip the front for increased airflow but keep the second layer sealed, to retain core heat. Clever stuff.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=BF+Email+-+Castelli+alpha+ros+jacket&amp;ued=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Fcastelli-alpha-ros-2-light-jacket\" target=\"_blank\">Buy the Castelli Alpha RoS Light Jacket from Wiggle</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Föhn Men’s Macro Synthetic Down Jacket – £114 (RRP £190) | SAVE £76!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"677\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-06-970x677.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-06-970x677.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-06-300x210.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-06-768x536.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-06-750x524.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-06-1140x796.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-06.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>A great choice whether you’re on a gravel adventure, on cheerleading duties at your local cyclocross race or getting to grips with some essential bike maintenance in a chilly garage. It’s lightweight, insulated, and made from feather-free, 100% recycled polyester – kind to the planet, and very kind to birds…</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=BF+Email+-+Fohn+macro+jacket&amp;ued=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Ffohn-mens-macro-synthetic-down-jacket\" target=\"_blank\">Buy the Föhn Men’s Macro Synthetic Down Jacket from Wiggle</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Up to 50% off cycling footwear!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>‘New shoes day’ is all the sweeter when you’ve picked them up for a steal. Check out the latest Black Friday deals on footwear <a href=\"http://www.wiggle.com/m/black-friday-cycle?categoryNames=Shoes\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Dhb Aeron Lab Carbon Road Shoe Dial – £90 (RRP £180) | SAVE £90!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-970x970.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-970x970.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-300x300.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-150x150.jpg 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-768x768.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-75x75.jpg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-350x350.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-750x750.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07-1140x1140.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-07.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>That’s right – a supple, supportive, lightweight racing slipper for half price. These elite-level shoes feature an Atop dial closure for precision fitting, a carbon sole for maximum power delivery, an advanced anti-slip ankle support and an aerodynamic upper. And they only weight 266g per shoe (in a UK size 8).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=BF+Email+-+dhb+aeron+shoe&amp;ued=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Fdhb-aeron-lab-carbon-road-shoe-dial\" target=\"_blank\">Buy the Dhb Aeron Lab Carbon Road Shoe Dial from Wiggle</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Dhb Neoprene Nylon Overshoes – £20 (RRP £35) | SAVE £15!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-970x970.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-970x970.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-300x300.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-150x150.jpg 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-768x768.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-75x75.jpg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-350x350.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-750x750.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08-1140x1140.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-08.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Overshoes are an absolute winter riding essential (unless you enjoy losing all feeling from your toes). And these are available at an unmissable price. Made from 3mm neoprene fabric, they’re the first line of defence against cold, windy, and wet conditions. A rear zip makes them simple to get on and off, and the added bonus is you get to keep your shoes clean. Win win, right?</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=BF+Email+-+dhb+neoprene+overshoes&amp;ued=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Fdhb-neoprene-nylon-overshoes\" target=\"_blank\">Buy the Dhb Neoprene Nylon Overshoes from Wiggle</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Up to 30% off bikes!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Winter is the ideal time to take the road less travelled, and these sizzling deals on off-road-ready machines are guaranteed to inspire adventures – for the whole family. Check out all of Wiggle’s Black Friday deals on bikes <a href=\"http://www.wiggle.com/m/black-friday-bikes\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Vitus Substance VR Gravel Bike – £629.99 (RRP £899.99) | SAVE £270!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-09-970x569.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-09-970x569.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-09-300x176.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-09-768x451.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-09-750x440.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-09-1140x669.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-09.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>The epitome of rugged readiness, the Vitus Substance VR is all set for your next off-road adventure. It features an alloy frame and carbon forks, a 1× groupset, 700c wheels with 40mm off-road-ready tyres, and mounts ready to receive all the luggage and bottles you’ll need for a bikepacking weekend.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1857&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=BF+Email+-+vitus+gravel+bike&amp;ued=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiggle.com%2Fp%2Fvitus-substance-vr-gravel-bike\" target=\"_blank\">Buy the Vitus Substance VR Gravel Bike from Wiggle</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Vitus 20 Kids Bike – £249.99 (RRP £349.99) | SAVE £100!</h3>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"808\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-10-970x808.jpg\" alt=\"Wiggle Black Friday week 1\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-10-970x808.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-10-300x250.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-10-768x639.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-10-750x624.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-10-1140x949.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/10/wiggle-black-friday-week-1-10.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>One to give the little ones a real treat on Christmas morning (if you have a decent hiding place for it between now and then!). This lightweight 20in-wheeler has a Shimano seven-speed groupset with thumb shifter, Tektro V-brakes and versatile tyres, and is the ideal way to build their confidence, whether on trails, roads or cycle paths.</p>\n\